videos.description: Eric Ayala fires a nice pass inside the pain to Bruno Fernando who rises up and throws down a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Maryland's Fernando hammers it home

videos.description: Bruno Fernando picks up the long pass in the paint and hammers a one-handed slam to give Maryland a 10-point lead over Northwestern.
videos.headline: Fernando attacks the rim for the Terrapins

videos.description: Anthony Gaines tips the ball away from Maryland and speeds to the other end for a nifty layup to bring Northwestern within single digits.
videos.headline: Gaines steals, rushes to the hoop for Northwestern bucket
